abstract: In a reflection of the market’s recent volatility, stocks fell in early trading Wednesday, giving back most of the gains from a 236-point rally in the Dow Tuesday, The New York Times’s Jack Healy reports.

headline.main: Markets Lose Gains After Bank Test Details Are Disclosed
